                Enable VOD</label>
            </div><!-- End of form-check div -->
##EOFEOFEOF7

    # Comment for VTP
    VTP_COMMENT="No of Ms between security credential verification using VTP. 0 = Verify every message; 1..65534 = No of milliseconds between verifications; 65535 = Disable VTP verification;"
